    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>A helper class containing a list of scalars. This is used for functions with scalar output parameters.
NOTE: If a function outputs an array, you must manually resize this to the correct size or risk undefined behavior.
NOTE: This stores booleans. Writing anything other than 0 or 1 to it can cause undefined behavior.
</verbatim> </para>
